Description: A fast paced death match map of small size. Several trigger_pushes allow speedy travel across the map.
 
Install: Unzip to "cstrike/maps" folder.
Uninstall: Delete "dm_climax_fng.bsp" and "dm_climax_fng.nav".

Created by: http://xiohexia.com


*note* Recently Updated. Download new version and overwrite old one.
